spirit:component.spirit:name: uberddr3_axi

spirit:enumeration.spirit:text: 1 (Enable self-refresh after 64 clock cycles of inactivity)
2 (Enable self-refresh after 128 clock cycles of inactivity)
3 (Enable self-refresh after 256 clock cycles of inactivity)

spirit:component.spirit:description: UberDDR3 is an open-source DDR3 memory controller designed for Xilinx FPGAs. It features a 4:1 memory interface with customizable parameters, allowing seamless integration with a wide range of DDR3 memory devices. The user interface is AXI4-compliant
